393278_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2eG9-8NiGJMQ7kNvgEviT_A&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCeS6G8QZgpZpoqXljXkw8PIePw4qXaPkRlsgvihhahAw&oe=676423E3"}, "display_name": "Monkey Doo", "keywords": ["free", "multiplayer", "gorilla", "social", "hangout"], "long_description": "# \u2744\ufe0f\u2603\ufe0fWinter Update! \n\n- New **Slide Surfer Gimmick** | Make ice slides and fly in the air! \n- Winter Battle Pass and a brand new Holiday Bundle!\n- Lobby & Bongos have a new Winter theme\n\n=================================================\n\n{8710703832373135}\n**About**\n# Live in the heart of the Bermuda Triangle with all your Monkey friends! Swing on vines, throw doo at your enemies, and climb everything! \n\n- Huge Maps: Explore the Bermuda Jungle, Floating Forests, Ancient Ruins, Lava Chasm, and more\n\n- Unique Gamemodes: Be the first to collect 10 bananas or work together to fend off hordes of crocs -- new modes are coming all the time\n\n- Monkey Apparel: Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo\n\n- Ruby Mines: Explore a seemingly endless set of tunnels filled with lore, new NPC's, and our Battle Pass! Unlock exclusive rewards like Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more with free and paid rewards! \n\n{2327501694315626}\n\nThemed Cosmetics & Hands-on Fun: Get your hands on... well, Hand cosmetics! Plus, a bunch of wacky, interactive items like things you can eat, press, and shake to your heart's content.\n\nHidden Treasures: Dive into a revamped store experience and hunt for secrets - like a mysterious portal leading to a hidden market. Plus, uncover new secrets via the plane!\n\nJump into the recently installed mining elevator to descend deep into the old ruby mines. Survive the **wrath of Xongo & save the Lost Souls** in Monkey Doo's all new Horror Mode!\n\n{9314948115205875}", "short_description": "\u2744\ufe0f\u2603\ufe0fWinter Update! \n\nLive in the heart of the Bermuda Triangle with all your Monkey friends! Swing on vines, throw doo at your enemies, and climb everything! \n\n- Huge Maps: Explore the Bermuda Jungle, Floating Forests, Ancient Ruins, Lava Chasm, and more\n\n- Unique Gamemodes: Be the first to collect 10 bananas or explore the lost mines and save souls -- new modes are coming all the time!\n\n- Monkey Apparel: Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo"}]}, "developer_name": "Continuum XR", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.clique.games/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.clique.games/terms", "publisher_name": "Clique Games ", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.monkeydoovr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1023770785722696"}, {"id": "1990104051447093"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "SOCIAL", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8760599894048010"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57568672_560063643469490_4099036854623523776_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VgPY4adn4zQQ7kNvgE3Ef6p&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCN-ovIHixPuugobzxCBDGTP4ZWx45VRWGBObSKGWEDfg&oe=676421AF"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Monkey Doo", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_